      • removeFolder

        public abstract void removeFolder()
        Removes a selected file from the file manager. The file is selected within the file manager, so there is a need to check that a file is selected. After the file is deleted, the manager makes sure the files are still in alphabetical/numerical order.

      • createFolder

        public abstract void createFolder(java.lang.String foldername)
        Creates a new folder directly insie of the eclass tool. After the folder is created, it is organized within the list of folders alphabetically or numerically.

      • renameFolder

        public abstract void renameFolder(java.lang.String new_name)
        Allows user to rename files. The selected file's name is changed to what the user inputs
